{
  "stem": "521.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then most everything was stolen, and we weren't much better off during the American-- after the American liberation than before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only thing is that we weren't shot dead by the Americans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How long did it take before you got to Hungary?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it has taken quite a long time because I was in that hospital for a while.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then later on, we had to go out and back for beg from Austrians for food because the food which we have received from the Americans wasn't satisfactory.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us dried peas, and it was mushy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were not ready to eat dried-- and so we went out, and we were begging for food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were getting some soup and some bread and something which we could eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, eventually, after about three weeks, four weeks, we were put on a train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And interestingly, they didn't leave us anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Americans put us on the train without any food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I don't know what did they think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no dining car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were only cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, of course, we have weren't 80 to a cattle wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were just side by side, as many Jews as they could accommodate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Still, in a sleeping bag.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrived to-- no, no, no, sorry, before we got to the train, we were-- no, the sleeping bag wasn't there anymore because as we had been liberated and we were taken to that barracks, to those barracks, before we went in there, they were getting rid of the lice.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So whatever I had, it was burnt.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
